description: Beautiful, well-appointed, remodeled, contemporary two - three bedroom, 1 1/2 bath condominium in attached, corner unit, three-family home in vibrant East Side of South Boston. Spacious and sunny with 1167 square feet of living space, laundry, and central heat/air. Perfect for family or roomate situation and conveniently located to restaurants, bars, gyms, public transportation, supermarket, shops and boutiques. And only a short stroll to the beaches and Castle Island! Terms Negotiable.
